===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|grammar}} A change in the form of a word to express different grammatical categories.
#: {{ux|en|an '''inflection''' for gender, number, or tense}}
# A change in [[pitch]] or [[tone]] of voice.
#: {{ux|en|If he's lying, his '''inflection''' changes.}}
# {{lb|en|mathematics}} A change in curvature from [[concave]] to [[convex]] or from convex to concave.
# A turning away from a straight course.
#: {{ux|en|'''inflection''' from the rules}}
